narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course was great. It radically changed the way I think about objects.

If you're interested in the topic, definitely do it. We got to go to the art gallery multiple times, the furniture room, Caseus to explore the artisanship of cheesemaking. It was a very doable work load with really interesting readings.
